"of the hierarchy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../library/tkinter.ttk.rst:1212
msgid ""
"Returns the identifier of *item*'s previous sibling, or '' if *item* is the "
"first child of its parent."
msgstr ""

#: ../../library/tkinter.ttk.rst:1218
msgid "Ensure that *item* is visible."
